# Sync UI Verification Checklist

## 1. Sync Diagnostics Tab (同期診断タブ)

| Check | Case | Expected UI |
|---|---|---|
| [ ] | **Success** (成功) | **Green Check Icon**<br>Message: "あなたのデータは安全にバックアップされています..." |
| [ ] | **Conflict** (競合) | **Yellow Warning Icon**<br>Message: "データの競合があります..." |
| [ ] | **Error** (エラー) | **Red Error Icon**<br>Message: "クラウドへの接続に失敗しましたが、データは端末内に安全に保存されています..." |
| [ ] | **Idle** (未同期) | **Grey Cloud Icon**<br>Message: "まだ同期が実行されていません..." |

## 2. Sync Status Indicator (ヘッダー表示)

| Check | Feature | Expected Behavior |
|---|---|---|
| [ ] | **Success Color** | Text color is **Green** (Teal-ish theme color). |
| [ ] | **Conflict Color** | Text color is **Yellow/Orange** (Prioritized over Green). |
| [ ] | **Error Color** | Text color is **Red**. |
| [ ] | **Timestamp: Today** | Format: `最終同期：今日 HH:mm` (e.g., 14:30) |
| [ ] | **Timestamp: Yesterday** | Format: `最終同期：昨日 HH:mm` |
| [ ] | **Timestamp: Older** | Format: `最終同期：YYYY/MM/DD HH:mm` |

## 3. Collapsible Details (詳細折りたたみ)

| Check | Action | Expected Behavior |
|---|---|---|
| [ ] | **Default State** | Technical stats (Graphs, Success Rate) are **HIDDEN**. |
| [ ] | **Click "Show Details"** | Section expands smoothly. Stats become visible. |
| [ ] | **Click "Hide"** | Section collapses. |

## 4. Conflict Guidance (競合誘導)

| Check | Scenario | Expected Flow |
|---|---|---|
| [ ] | **Conflict Detected** | Status Indicator shows Yellow Warning. |
| [ ] | **Menu Navigation** | User opens dropdown menu → Sees "Conflict Resolution" item. |
| [ ] | **Resolution UI** | Clicking item opens the Resolution Dialog with the list of conflicting cards. |

## 5. Persistence & Recovery (永続性と回復)

| Check | Scenario | Expected Behavior |
|---|---|---|
| [ ] | **App Restart** | Restarting the app does NOT lose the last sync status (Idle/Success/Error). |
| [ ] | **Recovery** | Fixing network → Retry Sync → Status immediately turns **Green**. |
